name: Parramatta

venue.name: Collaboratory
venue.under_18: At this Venue you must be accompanied by a Guardian at all times
venue.public_transport: Venue is 10 minute walk from Parramatta Station and there is a shuttle bus that goes from the station to the venue ever 15 minutes. Venue is also located right next to the Parramtta Ferry.
venue.parking: The is metered street parking available at the venue.
venue.public_transport_last: The last train going to central is at 12.30am.

catering: Snacks, Drinks, Tea and Coffee will all be provided. Main meals will be able to be purchased from local cafes etc.
